Package: CBSr
Type: Package
Title: Fits Cubic Bezier Spline Functions to Intertemporal and Risky Choice Data
Version: 1.0.5
Authors@R: person("Sangil", "Lee", email = "sangillee3rd@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Uses monotonically constrained Cubic Bezier Splines (CBS) to approximate latent utility functions in intertemporal choice and risky choice data.  
    Lee, S., Glaze, C. M., Bradlow, E. T., & Kable, J. W. (2020). Flexible Utility Function Approximation via Cubic Bezier Splines. psychometrika, 85(3), 716-737. https://doi.org/10.1007/s11336-020-09723-4
